            inputDate
            component
            CDK
	    Guide
        
    
    inputDate component development


        We a going to create the <inputDate>
        component that can take a value, process that value, and then push it
        back to the underlying model as a strongly typed Date object.
    


        The <inputDate> component allows to attach
        a converter in order to set the desired date format such as mm/dd/yyyy. So the component 
        could convert and validate the date entered by user. 
    
    
